                                sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                                text="&lt;p>The scientists who develop new medicines and the patients who live with disease all have one thing in common – tenacity. In their own words, hear how curiosity, creativity, and resilience help them achieve every major breakthrough and overcome each setback. Because good enough is never enough.&lt;/p>&#xa;"
