                                    sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                                    text="&lt;p>“Each disease impacts different patients in different ways, so the same treatment won’t work for everyone. And when science and our understanding of disease changes, so does our thinking on how we want to impact patients. The target is constantly evolving.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>We’re all working collectively to find that next frontier, to pioneer that next transformational medicine. Discovery scientists, chemists, pharmacists, statisticians and data scientists. It takes a village.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>Today’s needs are different from yesterday’s and tomorrow’s needs will be different still. We must keep pushing forward to help more patients live the way they want to live. There’s no better reward than to be part of that revolution.”&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>-&amp;nbsp;&lt;i>Mudra Kapoor, M.D.,Global Medical Affairs, Neuroscience, AbbVie&lt;/i>&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
